<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
        }

        .reset-link {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background-color: #ff5733;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .reset-link:hover {
            background-color: #e04a2c;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to proceed:</p>
    <a class="reset-link" href="{{resetLink}}" target="_blank">Reset Password</a>
    <p>This link will expire in {{expiresIn}} minutes.</p>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2025 Smash League. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
